{"tid":348524,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"求 治蟻 教學 ！ （蟻患）","createTime":"2017-08-05T18:45:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-06T03:21:20.000Z","uid":103380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"685744a0f685181e2ff8ec411b4cb49f833c7701","tid":348524,"uid":103380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T18:45:38.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打有清蟻經驗，屋企近排開始出現好多黑蟻，好高血，跑速又快，秒唔到，試過水攻，治標唔治本，第二朝又有，到依加起碼殺左兩三百隻，想問下有冇咩藥/味會驅蟻。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"873b010d44ab087d7f7c6bde6191f94712b9ee54","tid":348524,"uid":27396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T18:54:02.000Z","msg":"搵大笨象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35db7405d4533822c927ebe2ec643cd90ae6e38c","tid":348524,"uid":103380,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T18:55:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搵大笨象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n隻象會嬲死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8915f35e0a849e239c1bdb0b833cc173f4387e3f","tid":348524,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T19:22:28.000Z","msg":"睇下搵唔搵到佢地個竇<br />\n可能你屋企有個竇<br />\n<br />\n我地個陣係普通既蟻，好似搵漂白水狂漂佢地啲路<br />\n係咁灌水入佢屋企<br />\n最後用膠紙封住佢入口 點知佢地搵第二個窿入去<br />\n係咁用膠紙痴死佢地<br />\n<br />\n最後買左蟻粉 全部清晒"},{"pid":"e801a2146dd244dd98645b282a75339a405138cb","tid":348524,"uid":117751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T21:30:13.000Z","msg":"我都係咁呀巴打<br />\n殺極都有<br />\n個䆹仲要係廚房天花D廚櫃入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81c5adf38874caa286911c2b4ad6b9baabfd70bd","tid":348524,"uid":131836,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T23:21:09.000Z","msg":"前幾年廚房有好多蟻<br />\n有日嬲嬲地<br />\n走去跟蹤佢地<br />\n發現佢地多數由兩三個窿度爬出黎<br />\n之後我就用熱溶膠封左個窿<br />\n成班蟻就用其他窿入返去<br />\n到封晒d 窿之後<br />\n佢地就返唔到去<br />\n睇見都爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一定要留d 蟻係外面<br />\n因為佢地會帶你去搵其他入口<br />\n最後佢地無晒入口<br />\n你屋企就安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd0e489e0e5f861f6d84dd59a97561db1f723086","tid":348524,"uid":79839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T23:40:37.000Z","msg":"硼砂+糖+水 放係度唔洗理佢 幾日就清哂"},{"pid":"037c812565af57f9a66cf96515b9b7b110592e09","tid":348524,"uid":33938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T02:17:47.000Z","msg":"個蟻群係插穌入面 點搞好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  日日清極都仲有<br />\n又唔敢封住 驚d蟻係入面發癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00a9a879641a5463e93e073b2dba3f002652f838","tid":348524,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T02:46:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個蟻群係插穌入面 點搞好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  日日清極都仲有<br />\n又唔敢封住 驚d蟻係入面發癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係入面發癲會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4a396fa97eb4ec99dcfb07cb83bf733daa56f16","tid":348524,"uid":94794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T02:56:27.000Z","msg":"問隔離屋有無蜘蛛仔攞隻 返屋企放養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0246d2baf6ad2145b3c1743e02ee9afa6f8275ff","tid":348524,"uid":103380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T03:20:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇下搵唔搵到佢地個竇<br />\n可能你屋企有個竇<br />\n<br />\n我地個陣係普通既蟻，好似搵漂白水狂漂佢地啲路<br />\n係咁灌水入佢屋企<br />\n最後用膠紙封住佢入口 點知佢地搵第二個窿入去<br />\n係咁用膠紙痴死佢地<br />\n<br />\n最後買左蟻粉 全部清晒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我跟過佢地成粒鐘，我極懷疑係隔離屋啲蝻既廚房到惹過黎，即係個竇唔係我屋企 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想阻止佢爬黎我地屋企"},{"pid":"c35719180866d8f2cd731c7115a3408e4d8f03fd","tid":348524,"uid":103380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T03:21:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇下搵唔搵到佢地個竇<br />\n可能你屋企有個竇<br />\n<br />\n我地個陣係普通既蟻，好似搵漂白水狂漂佢地啲路<br />\n係咁灌水入佢屋企<br />\n最後用膠紙封住佢入口 點知佢地搵第二個窿入去<br />\n係咁用膠紙痴死佢地<br />\n<br />\n最後買左蟻粉 全部清晒</blockquote><br />\n想問蟻粉邊到買 藥房定惠康個啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好似啲甲由毒藥咁比啲蟻食就一天都光哂！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}